SUMMARY:Sakura Con 2026
DESCRIPTION:Presented by the Asia Northwest Cultural Education Association\, Sakura-Con is the oldest and most well attended anime convention in the Pacific Northwest. \nPlease join us for Sakura-Con 2026 where all of the excellent programming you’ve come to expect will be back in abundance. Gaming\, cosplay\, cultural panels\, dances\, concerts\, art contests\, AMV’s\, industry guests\, over 100\,000 square feet of exhibits hall\, guests of honor\, and more! \nPre-Register as a member now and save substantially versus at door prices. Remember that pre-registration helps ANCEA\, a state and federal non-profit organization\, put on the best Sakura-Con possible! As a member only event\, we all work together to keep our event “by fans\, for fans.” There are no additional fees for programming once you are at Sakura-Con\, including for autographs\, concerts\, theaters\, gaming\, etc. \nThe Asia-Northwest Cultural Education Association is a State and Federal 501c3 nonprofit corporation. As such\, our Form 990 are publicly available from the IRS. Here is the link you can use to request them: https://www.irs.gov/charities-non-profits/exempt-organizations-public-disclosure-obtaining-copies-of-documents-from-irs Please email info@sakuracon.org if you have further questions. Thank you.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/sakura-con-2026/
LOCATION:Seattle Convention Center\, 705 Pike Street\, Seattle\, Washington\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Screenshot-2026-03-31-110243.png
END:VEVENT
