SUMMARY:Cocktail\, Collaborate\, & Crank!
DESCRIPTION:Night owls! \n​Show up. Grab a cocktail. Open your laptop. Crank. \n​This is for founders\, solopreneurs\, freelancers\, professionals\, or anyone looking to get out of the house and focus on getting stuff done alongside people who’ll lift each other up and hold each other accountable. \n​If the moment moves you\, connect\, swap wins\, and maybe find your next collaborator. \n​​Our venue partners let us use their space for free — so we ask that you show some love and buy a cocktail\, an app\, something. Support local\, fuel yourself. Win-win. \n​​Ready\, set\, let’s build! \n​​Adam & Ryan\n​\n​PS. Locations rotate across North King County & South Snohomish County. Subscribe to our Luma page to know where we’ll be next!
