SUMMARY:AI for Innovators Happy Hour: Spot the Spoof
DESCRIPTION:Join us for good cheer and phenomenal conversations on how AI is shaping business owners\, entrepreneurs\, tech pros and the curious—right here in North King/South Snohomish County. \n​​Whether you’re a founder\, a corporate innovator\, or simply curious about the local tech and business scene\, you’ll find good company here. \nApple engineer or plumbing business owner…this means you! \n​​📍 Side Hustle\, Bothell\n​​📅 Thurs\, Apr 23\n​​⏰ 6-8 PM \n​​AGENDA:\n​6:00 PM – 6:30 PM: Networking and Grab a Drink\n​6:30 PM – 7:30 PM: Spot the Spoof & Open Discussion\n​*Can you tell which one is AI and which one is real?\n​*How is AI impacting fraud?\n*​How do you protect yourself?\n​​6:30 PM – 7:30 PM: Wrap-up Networking \n​WHO THIS IS FOR:\n1. ​Small business owners\, entrepreneurs\, and independents\n2. ​Finance\, security professionals\, and startup founders\n3. ​Anyone curious about how AI is changing the fraud landscape \n​WHAT YOU’LL WALK AWAY WITH:\n1. ​How to spot fraud flags before they become costly mistakes\n2. ​Practical strategies to mitigate your risk and protect your business\n3. ​Connections with local professionals navigating the same AI-driven challenges \n​​Drinks and connections await—RSVP now (attendance is FREE)! \n​​Adam & Ryan
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ai-for-innovators-happy-hour-spot-the-spoof/
