SUMMARY:ctrl+alt+create live: Vibe Coding for Everybody
DESCRIPTION:​You have ideas. We’ll help you build them! \n​This is a free\, ongoing community event series where technical and non-technical people build real software with AI\, together. \n​Entrepreneurs\, business owners\, students\, creatives\, engineers — everyone builds side by side. No coding experience needed. No gatekeeping. \n​Again\, you DO NOT NEED to be a developer to start developing software! We’ll show you how. \n​This doesn’t have to be a one-and-done event for you. Everyone is welcome to join us for all future events and we’ll be there to help you as you progress through your various projects and endeavors! \n​Register Here\, Now — Free. Spots are limited for in-person. \n​Bring a computer — Join us in Seattle or participate online from anywhere. \n​Learn — A guest educator kicks things off with a featured segment on a relevant AI or building topic. \n​Build + Showcase — You build for ~2 hours using AI tools that respond to plain English. At the end\, we demo work\, share what we made\, and give away a $100 Amazon Gift Card to one registered participant who completes the post-event survey.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ctrlaltcreate-live-vibe-coding-for-everybody-2/
