SUMMARY:TiE Entrepreneur Institute 2026
DESCRIPTION:TiE Entrepreneur Institute 2026 – Registrations Open! \nHave a startup idea but unsure how to turn it into a real company? \nTiE Seattle’s Entrepreneur Institute is designed to help aspiring and early-stage founders learn the fundamentals of building and scaling a startup—from idea validation and fundraising to go-to-market\, sales strategy\, and building strong teams. \nApr 29 – Jun 24\, 2026 | 5:00 PM (Virtual Sessions) \nLearn directly from successful founders\, seasoned executives\, and industry experts through practical\, interactive sessions. \nBonus for TiE Members:\n• 50% discount on the program\n• Access to the TiE global network\n• 1:1 mentorship from experienced entrepreneurs \nWhether you’re exploring an idea or already building\, this program will give you the frameworks\, insights\, and connections to move forward with confidence. \n👉 Register here:\nhttps://events.tie.org/TiEEntrepreneurInstitute2026#/ \nFeel free to share with founders and aspiring entrepreneurs in your network!
